rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0001
rows.name:
We should be able to take a ship
headed straight to Aletta from here.

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0002
rows.name:
That's great, but why's it got to be
a passenger ship?

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0003
rows.name:
Can't we travel with the emperor?
What's wrong with making a grand
entrance?

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0005
rows.name:
Though I may be traveling with Lord
Adel, I'm afraid my actions aren't
officially sanctioned.

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0006
rows.name: His Majesty's ship is a war vessel.

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0007
rows.name:
It would take considerable
negotiation before Iira granted
us docking privileges.

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0009
rows.name:
That attitude of yours is what gives us
so much trouble. You just don't stop to
think about the consequences, do you?

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0011
rows.name:
Behold the mighty Grail, wielder of
unthinkable power...and unparalleled
foolishness.

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0012
rows.name:
Hey, would you get off my case?!
I didn't even say anything!

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0013
rows.name:
Knock it off, you two. At the very
least, we've got a nice leisurely cruise
ahead of us, and that's something.

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0014
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]I'm excited to meet the resistance.
People who all look up to Addam...

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0015
rows.name:
Well then, if we're all agreed, let's
get on with it and talk to the captain,
shall we?
